Title: Reliance Water Controls 520-388-1106 multibloc 28mm 3.5 / 6bar
Description: Ideal for large installations requiring a high flow rate, the Reliance Water Controls 28mm 3.5/6 bar multibloc inlet control valve is a convenient one-piece fitting for reduced maintenance.
